These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
City: nizza, prague, marseilles, colone
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, october, march
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, photographer, musician, bartender
There 4 different types of food: tomato, onion, cherry, cranberry
 1. the photographer is not to the right of the project-manager##8
 2. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the project-manager is not to the left of the bartender##8
 5. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person eating onion and the photographer##2
 9. the person eating cranberry is the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
12. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
13. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
14. the person traveling to prague is the person eating cherry##1
15. the person traveling to prague is not the photographer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City         | nizza     | prague   | colone | marseilles |
| Birthday   | august | march   | february   | october  |
| Job         | photographer  | musician  | bartender  | project-manager |
| Food     | tomato    | cherry | onion     | cranberry    |

