.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
House: cottage, modern, art-deco, victorian
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, russian, mexican, pakistani
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, backgammon, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, ebony, mauve, blue
 1. the person playing backgammon is between the person who likes pink and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 2. the modern house is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8
 3. the modern house is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 4. the cottage house is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8
 5. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 6. the pakistani is not to the right of the victorian house##8
 7. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 8. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing poker is the person who likes ebony##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
11. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
12. the victorian house is on the left of the modern house##1
13. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
15. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3
16. the mexican is on the right of the colombian##1
17. the cottage house is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
18. the russian is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8
19. the victorian house is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| House      | cottage | art-deco | victorian  | modern  |
| Nationality          | pakistani     | russian | colombian | mexican  |
