 3. the fan of house is the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to new-york##2
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8
 7. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 9. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
11. the person who growstulip is not to the right of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
13. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
14. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
