 3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
 4. the architect is not the craftsman house##6
 5. the palace house is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 7. the architect is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 9. the townhouse house is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the cape-cod house##7
10. the townhouse house is not to the left of the project-manager##8
11. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
12. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the palace house##8
13. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
14. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
