 5. the palace house is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the tower house and the cottage house##7
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who likes black and the person who likes lavender##7
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
10. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
11. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
12. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
13. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes black##1
14. the person who likes black is not to the left of the cottage house##8
