15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to boston##1
16. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby           | skydiving | rock-climbing       | baking      | writing  |
| City   | edinburgh    | boston | hamburg   | rome   |
| Game   | scrabble   | snooker          | whist      | chess  |
| Food   | watermelon   | lime      | strawberry | broccoli |

